{
  "id": "RAW_7467883c",
  "title": "iOS 26.2 正式版来了，这些新特性值得关注",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4Mjg3MDAyMQ==&mid=2247601576&idx=2&sn=34fd36e3fcbe5115aa8ebe0640af37f6",
  "date": "2025-12-15 04:21:00",
  "author": "少数派",
  "siteName": "少数派",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">近日，Apple 面向所有适配机型的 iPhone 和 iPad 推送了 iOS / iPadOS 26 正式发布后的第二个大更新 iOS / iPadOS 26.2。在这个新版本中，Apple 为我们带来了诸多贴心的设置新选项和实用的应用新功能。接下来，就让我们一起来看看本次 iOS 26.2 版本的更新内容吧。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">提醒事项</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">不知道你有没有和我一样的困扰：想在下周一晚上 8 点抢购演唱会门票，或者本周日上午 0 点抢购喜欢的服装品牌新品，但是提醒事项的提醒通知不够有「侵略性」，在忙的时候很容易忽视，而闹钟又只能设置当天的提醒，所以经常陷入两难。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在 iOS 26.2 更新中，Apple 为提醒事项新增了一个「紧急选项」，打开后会自动启用日期和时间选项，设置好我要提醒的日期和时间后，提醒事项会全屏提醒，界面和音效就和闹钟一样，可以达到与之前完全不同的提醒效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117912\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.08125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=56655d71&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3LCpsyXWDS0ibdHuAicTsJwgPdEyElTmZeM4Wk7hXq8LsjPu8SSWf4JEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在提醒界面中有「稍后提醒」和「滑动以停止」两个选项，后者就不用多说了，如果点击了「稍后提醒」按钮，那么系统会在锁屏界面上显示一个倒计时小组件，包含了下一次提醒时间的倒计时，我们可以点击「重新定时」按钮来进入到该提醒事项的详情页重新设置「紧急」提醒的日期或者时间，也可以直接在小组件上勾选完成当前提醒事项。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117915\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.08125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e922fbf6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3gibcMxozg0D67bSBEyZrev2Xm7Bp8vbvTE9JrPqiaoibxHyoBcdxO9qGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">AirDrop</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Apple 的 AirDrop 是大家都很喜欢的一个功能，它可以非常方便地与别人分享照片、文件等内容。不过，AirDrop 也有一方面不太灵活，那就是设置分享的对象。之前，AirDrop 仅提供了所有人和仅限联系人两种选项，所以很多情况下我不想和非联系人 AirDrop 时就只能打开「所有人」的开关，可能会遇到一些人恶意或者无意 AirDrop 到我的设备上的情况。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在新版本中，Apple 为 iOS 26 新增了一个「一次性代码」功能，将这个代码告知对方后，可以临时建立 AirDrop 连接并传送文件，只需在两台升级到 iOS 26.2、没有互相留存通讯录的 iPhone 上开始 AirDrop 流程即可设置。在「设置」&gt;「通用」&gt;「隔空投送」中，还可以看到一个「管理已知隔空投送联系人」的选项，这个联系人列表中的联系人都可以在 30 天内获得 AirDrop 共享对象可见。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117916\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" style=\"width: 365px;height: 794px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c02469c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3YR1qCv2GGtkc0xrlBsQibvDjKPUgQTicPzwgRa5vQWXrhzEgricdXzHKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">其它更新</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">锁屏界面的时钟，在新版本中可以选择「玻璃」和「实线」两种样式，其中「玻璃」样式下可以通过滑条无极调节透明度、反光度等显示效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117913\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7214285714285714\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e86af87e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj38j2MnJ9l1ic02loU0WvWDdMN0nbygJ1P2icjEuTbA1IVbXMhfP9xwozQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Apple Music 支持了离线歌词的功能，即使 iPhone 没有连接到 WiFi 或者蜂窝网络，也可以实时查看已离线的歌词。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117911\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.08125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0309398d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3g4RXw052d3vjIFicUD2EWCOGCAiaOw1j6iaSGZCD1Aciah6RmAUlsUVQrQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Apple 在新版本重新划分了睡眠评分，从原先的 0-29、30-49、50-69、70-89、90-100 被重新划分为 0-40、41-60、61-80、81-95、96-100 这几个区间，也意味着想获得最高档的评分比以前更难了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117921\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6376aeab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3JpY4TZc4e8zp7DUWRySEtfLOqUU6qSOypfLMOHTXibfob7iceqIknmvw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">播客应用获得了三个全新的功能，分别是自动创建章节、查看和订阅其他提及的播客节目、快速访问链接内容。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117914\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.08125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6712307e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3fYibo6UgEcib10yYibbWZfLWtLoZ8v3iaK1W8K8JYV5ICZ3jumX6pGayLA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">密码设置中新增了一个排除询问保存密码的网站白名单功能，打开这些网站时不再会被询问是否要保存当前的用户名和密码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117918\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.08125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2604bf42&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3K79bLKdRbib38prRlfhBNEJs0YFVRfqV45bp7vakkYrBWjhmy4p8MGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">无边记应用支持了新增和编辑表格功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100117917\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7214285714285714\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5afaaeba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3nnibtuHFhHFCYgPbtHSSltiaJFqUs7iacuukmj3ibZtDiaYFRLiaMH99t26A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在「设置」&gt;「辅助功能」&gt;「音频与视觉」&gt;「闪烁以示提醒」中新增了「屏幕」和「同时」的选项，开启「闪烁以示提醒」后，我们现在可以选择让手机背面的 LED 闪烁、屏幕闪光或者两者同时触发来进行提醒，以防你错过非常重要的通知。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100117920\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1771ed3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3fsu5fOIsFIxrDX7UCvJVqBebkoL0iav0bmP6P8lU2xaMIpqnVXYJC8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">测距仪应用中的水平仪部分更新了 UI，原先的两个白色圆圈被两个液态玻璃气泡所代替。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100117919\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=996ff005&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj32Kj6xeLgjLdiccy1WsSm1qQ93MO5uMjxMCjVicZYicBxqibgAMO94Y1X8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">游戏应用中的资料库新增了一个「大小」排序选项，支持了游戏手柄导航功能以及实时查看挑战分数。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100117922\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f283c262&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRg6H2FicJCAtIdhwVbljELj3pzbiauQX5dVicOHHx8YqsK3GFB6KBQnx9gjQKBVyDiaZz7tYvwYwMUfhg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">日本区域的改变</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">虽然说和我们中国大陆用户没有直接的关联，我们不妨也来简单地了解一下Apple 在 iOS 26.2 中针对日本用户的调整，也许以后会有更多的国家和地区会跟进：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">首先，Apple 允许日本用户更换语音助手，Siri 不再是唯一的选择，用户还可以使用 Gemini、Alexa 等其它语音助手。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">其次，Apple 在系统引导界面中加入了默认搜索引擎的设置界面，会让用户在正式进入系统前就可以从 Google、Yahoo、Bing、DuckDuckGo 和 Ecosia 中进行选项。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最后，Apple 也允许日本用户和之前的欧盟用户一样安装第三方应用市场。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">以上就是本次 iOS 26.2 的全部更新内容了，没有特别重大的变化，不过也获得了一些实用的功能更新。如果你在本次更新中还发现了其它有意思的变化，欢迎在评论区一起交流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/104408?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social\" target=\"_blank\">https://sspai.com/post/104408?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者：Vanilla</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">责编：waychane</span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文详细介绍了 iOS 26.2 正式版带来的多项新功能和改进，包括提醒事项的紧急选项、AirDrop 的一次性代码、锁屏界面的个性化设置以及日本区域的系统级调整等，提升了用户体验和系统灵活性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文详细介绍了 iOS 26.2 正式版带来的多项新功能和改进，包括提醒事项的紧急选项、AirDrop 的一次性代码、锁屏界面的个性化设置以及日本区域的系统级调整等，提升了用户体验和系统灵活性。",
  "summary": "文章全面回顾了 iOS 26.2 正式版本的更新亮点。首先，在提醒事项中引入了“紧急选项”，使其可以像闹钟一样全屏提醒，有效解决了重要事项提醒易被忽视的问题。其次，AirDrop 新增“一次性代码”功能，增强了文件分享的隐私性和灵活性，同时优化了已知联系人管理。此外，文章还提及了锁屏时钟样式、Apple Music 离线歌词、健康应用睡眠评分调整、播客应用功能增强、密码自动保存排除白名单、无边记表格支持、辅助功能闪烁提醒选项、测距仪 UI 更新以及游戏应用库排序等一系列细微但实用的改进。最后，关注了日本区域的突破性变化，包括允许更换语音助手、默认搜索引擎设置以及安装第三方应用市场，预示着 Apple 在特定市场策略上的调整。",
